          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Cross sections ratio He3/Li6 was defined as:",
                " =(T/Tnorm)*(SIGhe/SIGli))*K, where",
                "T=Nhe/Nli, Tnorm=(Nhe/Nli)norm - ratios of counting",
                "numbers of two detectors ( background subtracted) at",
                "investigated energy and normalization energy (index",
                "norm);",
                "K=(EPSli/EPShe)/(EPSli/EPShe)norm,",
                "where EPS - detector efficiency for Li and He at",
                "investigated energy and normalization energy.",
                "Normalization point was in energy range 168-259 eV,",
                "where Li6 and He3 cross sections are described by",
                "formulas:",
                "149.5/sqrt(E), 848.6/sqrt(E)*(1+1.5E-3*sqrt(E)),",
                "respectively."
              ]
            }
          ],
